PrecisAmendment to the EARLY DEPARTURE INCENTIVE PROGRAM ORDER whereby Airports Group employees of the Department of Transport at Watson Lake Airport or Whitehorse Airport who have not received an early departure incentive offer before February 23, 1996, will no longer be eligible for such an offer.
